'''勒羅伊'''（{{lang|en|'''LeRoy'''}}）為[[美国|美国]][[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]][[科菲縣_(堪薩斯州)|科菲縣]]轄下的城市。根據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，此城市人口有561人<ref name="Census2010">{{cite web|title=2010 City Population and Housing Occupancy Status|url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table|publisher=U.S. Census Bureau|accessdate=February 3, 2012|archive-date=2011-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721034521/http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==歷史==
勒羅伊設立於1855年，城市名字則以[[伊利諾伊州|伊利諾伊州]]的城市[[勒羅伊_(伊利諾伊州)|勒羅伊]]命名<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA165#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Biennial Report of the Board of Directors of the Kansas State Historical Society | publisher=Kansas State Printing Plant | author=Kansas State Historical Society | year=1916 | pages=165 | access-date=2016-05-15 | archive-date=2014-07-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706195615/http://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA165#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

此城市第一所郵政局於1856年3月20日開設<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county:CF |title=Kansas Post Offices, 1828-1961 (archived) |publisher=Kansas Historical Society |accessdate=6 June 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131009123958/http://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county:CF |archivedate=2013-10-09 }}</ref>。

==地理==
勒羅伊坐落於北緯38度5分2秒、西經95度37分59秒（亦可表示為38.083958, -95.633139）處<ref name="GR1">{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2011-04-23|date=2011-02-12|title=US Gazetteer files: 2010, 2000, and 1990|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060720110047/http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|archive-date=2006-07-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。根據[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]的資料，此城市總面積為{{convert|2.15|sqkm|sqmi|2}}，其中{{convert|2.12|sqkm|sqmi|2}}為陸地，{{convert|0.03|sqkm|sqmi|2}}為水域<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2012-07-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

===氣候===
夏季溼熱、冬季不甚乾冷為此地區的氣候特徵。根據[[柯本气候分类法|柯本气候分类法]]，勒羅伊的氣候屬於[[副热带湿润气候|副热带湿润气候]]（氣候地圖簡寫「Cfa」）<ref>[http://www.weatherbase.com/weather/weather-summary.php3?s=576441&cityname=Le+Roy%2C+Kansas%2C+United+States+of+America&units= Climate Summary for LeRoy, Kansas]</ref>。

